== Russian ==
'''выковы́ривать''' (vykovýrivat') {{italbrac|imperfective|transitive}}

=== Word formation ===
''prefix'' [[вы-]] + ''root'' [[ковыр]] (''from'' [[ковырять]]) + [[-ива-]] + [[-ть]]

=== Verb ===
# to [[pick]] [[out]], to [[pluck]] [[out]], to [[take]] [[out]], to [[pull out]], to [[extract]] [[something|smth.]] while digging up, rummaging, delving.

